@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### 0. Register Admin (ทำแค่ครั้งแรกครั้งเดียว)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "admin01",
    "password": "password1234"
