### 1. Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "admin01",
    "password": "password1234"
}

### 2. Get Users (ต้อง Login ก่อน)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

### 3. Logout (Reset Client)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout